 ɔde ne tumi nante omununkum mu.

Onyankopɔn a ɔwɔ hɔ daa yɛ wo dwanekɔbea;
 nʼabasa a ɛwɔ hɔ daa no kura wo.
 Ɔbɛpam wʼatamfoɔ afiri wʼanim;
 Ɔno na ɔteaam sɛ, ‘Sɛe wɔn!’

