II Samuel:
Hwɛ sɛdeɛ mesu woɔ, me nua Yonatan;
 Ao, hwɛ ɔdɔ a mede dɔɔ woɔ!
 Na wo dɔ a wode dɔɔ me no mu dɔ;
 emu dɔ sene mmaa dɔ!

Wɔankyekyere wo nsa;
 wɔangu wo nan nkɔnsɔnkɔnsɔn.
 Dabi, wɔdii wo awu;
 amumuyɛfoɔ atirimpɔ so adeɛ.”
 Nnipa no nyinaa suu Abner bio.

Na asase wosoeɛ na ɛhinhimeɛ;
 ɔsoro fapem wosoeɛ;
 wɔwosoeɛ, nʼabufuo enti.

Wisie firii ne hwene mu;
 ogyaframa firii nʼanom;
 na egyasramma dɛre firii mu.

“Womaa me nkonimdie wɔ wɔn a wɔbɔ me kwaadu so.
 Woahwɛ sɛ mɛyɛ amanaman sodifoɔ;
 na nnipa a mennim wɔn som me.

“Wode nkonimdie akɛseɛ ama wo ɔhene;
 woda ɔdɔ a ɛnsa da adi kyerɛ deɛ woasra no ngo,
 wode kyerɛ Dawid, ne nʼasefoɔ afebɔɔ.”

Wɔn a aka a wɔfra Aduasa no mu nie:
  Yoab nuabarima Asahel;
 Dodo a ɔfiri Betlehem babarima Elhanan;

I Chronicles:
Nnipa a na wɔka Dawid nnɔmmarima no ho nie:
  Yoab nuabarima Asahel;
 Dodo babarima Elhanan a ɔfiri Betlehem;

Eliel a ɔfiri Mahawi;
 Elnaam mmammarima Yeribai ne Yosawia;
 Yitma a ɔfiri Moab;

Na deɛ ɔtua wɔn ano yɛ Semaa a ɔfiri Gibea no babarima Ahieser. Na ne nuabarima ne Yoas a ɔyɛ nʼabadiakyire. Yeinom ne nnɔmmarima no nkaeɛ:
 Asmawet mmammarima Yesiel ne Pelet;
 Beraka ne Yehu a wɔfiri Anatot;

Na wɔn edin ne:
 Otni, Refael, Obed ne Elsabad;
 na wɔn abusuafoɔ Elihu ne Semakia nso yɛ mmɔdemmɔfoɔ.

Mmusuakuo no ne wɔn ntuanofoɔ nie:
  Ruben abusuakuo: Sikri babarima Elieser;
 Simeon abusuakuo: Maaka babarima Sefatia;

Nehemiah:
nanso, nnipa no bi a wɔfiri Yuda ne Benyamin mu no sane kɔtenaa Yerusalem.
