 Usia babarima Ataia, Sakaria babarima, Amaria babarima, Sefatia babarima, Mahalalel babarima a ɔfiri Peres abusua mu;

Job:
Saa ɛda no nnuru sum;
 mma Ɔsoro Onyankopɔn nhwehwɛ akyire kwan;
 mma hann biara ntɔ ngu so.

Ma esum ne owusum nnye no mfa;
 ma omununkum nkata so;
 na esum mmunkam ne hann so.

Ma esum kabii nnye saa anadwo no mfa;
 ma wɔnyi saa anadwo no mfiri asranna so
 na wɔmmfa nhyɛ ɔbosome biara mu.

Ma nʼanɔpa nsoromma nnuru sum;
 na ɔntwɛne adekyeeɛ kwa
 a ɔnhunu anɔpa owia nsensaneɛ a ɛdi ɛkan,

Otumfoɔ agyan no awɔ me mu,
 me honhom nom ano awuduro no;
 wɔahyehyɛ Onyankopɔn ahunahuna nyinaa atia me.

“Ɛno enti meremmua mʼano;
 mɛfiri me honhom ahoyera mu akasa,
 mɛfiri me kra ɔyea mu anwiinwii.

“Ɛwom sɛ medi bem deɛ,
 nanso memmu me ho;
 abrabɔ afono me.

“Abrabɔ afono me;
 enti mɛka mʼasɛm a meremfa hwee nsie
 na mɛkasa afiri me kra yeadie mu.

Wode adansefoɔ foforɔ bɛtia me
 na woma wʼabofuo ano yɛ den wɔ me so;
 wʼakodɔm tu ba me so ɛberɛ biara.

Amumuyɛfoɔ ani bɛfira,
 wɔrentumi nnwane;
 na wɔn anidasoɔ bɛdane owuo ahomeguo.”

Wode nkyehoma gu me nan;
 wohwɛ mʼanammɔnkwan nyinaa so yie
 na wode ahyɛnsodeɛ ayeyɛ mʼanammɔn mu.

Woahyehyɛ onipa nkwa nna;
 woahyɛ nʼabosome dodoɔ ato hɔ
 na woahyɛ no ɛberɛ a ɔrentumi ntra.

saa ara na onipa tɔ fam na ɔnsɔre bio;
 ɛnkɔsi sɛ ɔsoro bɛtwam no, nnipa rensɔre
 na wɔrennyane wɔn mfiri wɔn nna mu.

Esum bɛduru wɔn;
 ogyaframa bɛkusa wɔn mman,
 na Onyankopɔn anom ahomeguo bɛsoa wɔn akɔ.

Onyankopɔn to hyɛ me so tete me wɔ nʼabufuo mu
 na ɔtwɛre ne se gu me so;
 deɛ ɔne me anya no pɔkyere nʼani hwɛ me.

Nnipa bue wɔn ano di me ho fɛw;
 wɔbɔ me sotorɔ de bu me animtiaa
 na wɔka wɔn ho bɔ mu de tia me.

Na biribiara kɔ yie ma me, nanso ɔdwerɛɛ me;
 ɔsɔɔ me kɔn mu, too me hwee hɔ.
 Ɔde me asi nʼani so;

Nʼakodɔm ba anibereɛ so;
 wɔsisi mpie de tia me
 na wɔtwa me ntomadan ho hyia.

Wɔbɛtwe bɛmma no firi nʼakyi,
 ano hyɛnhyɛn no bɛfiri ne brɛboɔ mu.
 Ehu bɛba ne so;

Bɔnhwa mu dɔteɛ yɛ no dɛ;
 nnipa nyinaa di nʼakyi,
 na ɛdɔm a wɔntumi nkan wɔn di nʼanim.

Ahiafoɔ no yɛ wɔn adwuma pɛ aduane
 te sɛ ɛserɛ so mfunumu no;
 asase wesee no so na wɔnya aduane ma wɔn mma.

Sɛ adekyeɛ hann no kɔ a, owudifoɔ no sɔre
 na ɔkum ohiani ne mmɔborɔni;
 adesaeɛ mu, ɔwiawia ne ho sɛ ɔkorɔmfoɔ.

Ɔwaresɛefoɔ twɛn ɛberɛ a adeɛ resa;
 ɔka sɛ, ‘obiara renhunu me,’
 na ɔde nʼanim hinta.

Esum mu na nnipa bubu apono wura afie mu,
 na awiaberɛ mu no, wɔtoto wɔn ho ɛpono mu;
 wɔne hann nni hwee yɛ.

“Nanso wɔte sɛ ahuro a ɛtɛ nsuo ani;
 wɔadome wɔn kyɛfa wɔ asase no so,
 enti obiara nnkɔ bobe nturo no mu.

Wɔma wɔn so berɛ tiawa bi, na afei wɔnni hɔ bio;
 wɔbrɛ wɔn ase boaboa wɔn ano sɛ nnipa nyinaa;
 wɔtwitwa wɔn gu te sɛ aburoo ti.

Yeinom yɛ ne nnwuma mfeafeaho;
 ɔka asomusɛm brɛoo kyerɛ yɛn!
 Na hwan na ɔbɛtumi ate ne tumi mmobɔmu no ase.”

Onipa ma esum ba awieeɛ;
 na ɔhwehwɛ kɔ akyirikyiri asase mu
 kɔpɛ dadeben wɔ esum kabii mu.

Na ɔka kyerɛɛ onipa sɛ,
 “  suro, ɛno ne nyansa;
 na sɛ wɔkyiri bɔne a, wowɔ nteaseɛ.”

Mebɔɔ ɛkwan maa wɔn na metenaa ase sɛ wɔn ɔhene;
