 Ɛbɛda mpan firi awoɔ ntoatoasoɔ akɔsi awoɔ ntoatoasoɔ;
 obiara remfa ho bio koraa.

Anweatam ne asase a awo no ani bɛgye;
 ɛserɛ bɛdi ahurisie na ayɛ frɔmm.
 Te sɛ nhwiren no,

ɛbɛpae ayɛ fɛɛfɛɛfɛ;
 ɛbɛdi ahurisie na ɛde anigyeɛ ateam.
 Wɔde Lebanon animuonyam bɛma anweatam no.
 Ɛbɛyɛ sɛ Karmel ne Saron ahoɔfɛ;
 wɔbɛhunu   animuonyam,
 yɛn Onyankopɔn tumi no.

Ka kyerɛ wɔn a wɔn akoma atu no sɛ,
 “Monhyɛ mo ho den, na monnsuro;
 mo Onyankopɔn bɛba,
 ɔde aweretɔ bɛba;
 ananmuhyɛ a ɛfiri ɔsoro
 bɛba abɛgye mo nkwa.”

Na ɔkwantempɔn bɛda hɔ;
 wɔbɛfrɛ no Ahoteefoɔ Kwan.
 Wɔn a wɔn ho nteɛ rentu ɛkwan wɔ so;
 ɛbɛda hɔ ama wɔn a wɔnante saa Ɛkwan no so;
 amumuyɛfoɔ nkwaseafoɔ rennante nante so.

Mede ntoboaseɛ twɛneeɛ kɔsii ahemadakye,
 nanso wɔbobɔɔ me nnompe mu te sɛ gyata;
 awia ne anadwo wotwaa me nkwa so.

Damena rentumi nkamfo wo;
 owuo rentumi nto wo ayɛyi nnwom;
 wɔn a wɔsiane kɔ amena mu no
 rentumi nya anidasoɔ wɔ wo nokorɛ mu bio.

Ampa ara aman no te sɛ nsuo sope wɔ bokiti mu;
 wɔde wɔn toto mfuturo a ɛgu nsania so;
 ɔkari nsupɔ te sɛ deɛ ɛyɛ mfuturo muhumuhu.

Aman nyinaa nsɛ hwee wɔ nʼanim;
 ɔbu wɔn adehunu bi
 a wɔnka hwee.

Nsupɔ no ahunu na wɔbɔ hu;
 nsase ano ho popo.
 Wɔtwi bɛn, na wɔba anim;

Nsuro, na me ne wo wɔ hɔ;
 mma wʼabasam mmu, na mene wo Onyankopɔn.
 Mɛhyɛ wo den, na mɛboa wo;
 mede me tenenee nsa nifa bɛpagya wo.

Nanso, monnka hwee,
 na mo nnwuma ho nni mfasoɔ;
 deɛ ɔfa mo no yɛ akyiwadeɛ.

Hwɛ, wɔn nyinaa yɛ atorofoɔ!
 Wɔn nneyɛeɛ nka hwee;
 wɔn nsɛsodeɛ yɛ mframa ne basabasayɛ nko ara.

Demmire a ayɛ mmerɛ no, ɔremmu mu.
 Kanea ntoma a ɛnnɛre yie no, ɔrennum.
 Nokorɛ mu na ɔbɛda tenenee adi;

Ma anweatam ne ɛso nkuro mma wɔn nne so;
 ma atenaeɛ a Kedar te soɔ no nsɛpɛ wɔn ho.
 Ma nnipa a wɔwɔ Sela nto anigye dwom;
 ma wɔn nteam mfiri mmepɔ no atifi!

Na afei, sei na   seɛ,
 deɛ ɔbɔɔ woɔ, Ao Yakob
 deɛ ɔnwonoo woɔ, Ao Israel;
 “Nsuro na magye wo;
 mabɔ wo din afrɛ wo; woyɛ me dea.

Nsuro, ɛfiri sɛ, meka mo ho;
 mede wo mma bɛfiri apueeɛ fam aba
 na maboa wɔn ano afiri atɔeɛ fam.

Monhwehwɛ deɛ atwam no mu bio mma me,
 momma yɛmmɔ mu ntonto adwene wɔ asɛm no ho;
 ka wʼasɛm a ɛkyerɛ sɛ wonni fɔ no.

Obi bɛka sɛ, ‘Meyɛ   dea’;
 ɔfoforɔ bɛfrɛ ne ho sɛ Yakob;
 bio ɔfoforɔ bɛtwerɛ ne nsa ho sɛ, ‘  dea,’
 na wafa edin Israel.
 , Ɛnyɛ Ahoni

Ɔtomfoɔ fa nʼatondadeɛ
 ɔde hyehyɛ egyasramma mu;
 ɔde asaeɛ bobɔ so yɛ no ohoni,
 ɔde nʼabasamu ahoɔden mmorosoɔ na ɛyɛ;
 ɛkɔm de no na ɔyɛ mmrɛ;
 ɔnnom nsuo enti ɔtɔ baha.

Ɛyɛ deɛ onipa de sɔ ogya;
 ɔde ebi ka ne ho hye,
 ɔde bi sɔ ogya to burodo.
 Nanso ɔde ebi sene onyame nso na ɔsɔre no;
 ɔyɛ ohoni na ɔkoto no.

Wonnim hwee, na wɔnte hwee ase;
 wɔasram wɔn ani so enti wɔnhunu adeɛ,
 wɔato wɔn adwene mu enti wɔnte hwee ase.

Nsõ na ɔdie, nnaadaa akoma ma no yera kwan;
 ɔrentumi nye ne ho, anaa ɔrentumi nka sɛ,
 “Deɛ mekura wɔ me nsa nifa yi nnyɛ atorɔ anaa?”

Meyɛ hann, na mebɔ esum.
 Mede yiedie ba na mede ɔhaw ba;
 Me,  , na meyɛ yeinom nyinaa.

“Mo ɔsorosoro, monhwie tenenee ngu fam;
 momma ɛmfiri omununkum mu ntɔ
 momma asase mu mmue kɛseɛ,
 na nkwagyeɛ mpue mfiri mu,
 na tenenee ne no nnyini;
 Me,   na mayɛ.

Menkasaa wɔ kɔkoam,
 mfiri asase so baabi a aduru sum;
 manka ankyerɛ Yakob asefoɔ sɛ,
 ‘Sɛ mohwehwɛ me a monnhunu me.’
 Me  , meka nokorɛ no;
 meka deɛ ɛyɛ.

“Monnane mmra me nkyɛn na monnya nkwa,
 mo a mowɔ asase ano nyinaa;
 ɛfiri sɛ mene Onyankopɔn, na obiara nni hɔ.

Wɔbɔ mu kuntun, bɔ wɔn mu ase;
 wɔntumi nsi amanehunu ano,
 wɔn ankasa kɔ nkoasom mu.

Monkae nneɛma a atwam no, teteete nneɛma no;
 Me ne Onyankopɔn, na obi nni hɔ;
 Me ne Onyankopɔn, na obiara nte sɛ me.

Mɛfrɛ anomaa a ɔkyere mmoa afiri apueeɛ fam;
 afiri akyirikyiri asase so, onipa a ɔbɛhyɛ me botaeɛ ma.
 Deɛ maka no, ɛno na mɛma aba mu;
 deɛ madwene ho no, ɛno na mɛyɛ.

Nokorɛm, wɔte sɛ nnyentia;
 ogya bɛhye wɔn.
 Na wɔntumi nnye wɔn ankasa ho
 mfiri egyadɛreɛ ano den no ho.
 Ogyasramma biara nni ha a ɛbɛka wo hye;
 ogya biara nni ha a wɔbɛtena ho ato.

Nneɛma a atwam no medii ɛkan kaeɛ,
 mebɔɔ nkaeɛ, na medaa no adi;
 afei mpofirim mekekaa me ho na ɛbaa mu.

Wonteeɛ, na wontee aseɛ;
 ɛfiri tete nyinaa wʼaso asi.
 Na menim sɛ woyɛ ɔfatwafoɔ;
 wɔfrɛɛ wo otuatefoɔ firi yafunu mu.

Medin enti metwentwɛne mʼabufuo so;
 mʼayɛyie enti meyi firii wo so,
 sɛdeɛ mentwa wo ntwene.

“Tie me, Ao, Yakob,
 Israel a mafrɛ no;
 Me ne no;
 Me ne Ahyɛaseɛ ne Awieeɛ.

Osukɔm anne wɔn ɛberɛ a ɔdii wɔn anim, wɔ anweatam ahodoɔ so no,
 ɔmaa nsuo firi ɔbotan mu ba maa wɔn;
 ɔpaee ɔbotan no mu, maa nsuo tue firii mu.

Momfa anigyeɛ nteam, Ao ɔsoro;
 di ahurisie, Ao asase;
 monto nnwom, Ao mmepɔ!
 Na   kyekye ne nkurɔfoɔ werɛ,
 na ɔbɛhunu nʼamanehunufoɔ mmɔbɔ.

Ahemfo bɛyɛ mo agyanom nsiananmu,
 na wɔn ahemaa ayɛ maamenom a wɔbɛhwɛ mo.
 Wɔbɛkoto mo a wɔn anim butubutu fam;
 wɔbɛtafere mo nan ase mfuturo.
 Afei mobɛhunu sɛ me ne  ;
 Wɔn a wɔn ani da me so no, merenni wɔn hwammɔ.”

Otumfoɔ   abue mʼaso
 na menyɛɛ otuatefoɔ;
 na mensanee mʼakyi.

“Montie me, mo a mopɛ tenenee akyiri kwan;
 na mohwehwɛ  ;
 Monhwɛ ɔbotan a wɔtwaa mo firii mu no
 ne abopaebea a wɔtuu mo firii hɔ no;

“Montie me, me nkurɔfoɔ;
 monyɛ aso mma me, me ɔman:
 Mmara no bɛfiri me nkyɛn akɔ;
 na mʼatɛntenenee bɛyɛ hann ama aman no.

Ɛrenkyɛre, wɔbɛgyaa nneduafoɔ ahufoɔ no;
 wɔrenwuwu wɔ afiase amena mu,
 na aduane remmɔ wɔn.

Na yei ne deɛ Otumfoɔ Awurade seɛ:
 “Ɛberɛ bi me nkurɔfoɔ kɔɔ Misraim kɔtenaa hɔ;
 akyire no Asiria bɛhyɛɛ wɔn so.

“Trɛ wo ntomadan no mu;
 twe wo ntomadan ntwamu no mu,
 nnyae yɛ;
 toa wo ntampehoma no so,
 bobɔ wo mpɛɛwa no so ma ɛntim yie.

Ɛfiri sɛ wobɛtrɛ akɔ nifa ne benkum;
 wʼasefoɔ bɛgye aman afa
 na wɔatena wɔn nkuropɔn a asɛe no so.

Israel awɛmfoɔ yɛ anifirafoɔ,
 wɔn mu biara nni nimdeɛ;
 wɔn nyinaa yɛ nkraman mum,
 wɔntumi mmobɔ mu;
 wɔdeda hɔ na wɔsoso daeɛ,
 nna yɛ wɔn dɛ.

Wɔyɛ nkraman a wɔpɛ aduane yie;
 wɔnnidi mmee da.
 Wɔyɛ nnwanhwɛfoɔ a wɔnni nteaseɛ;
 wɔn nyinaa fa wɔn ɛkwan,
 obiara pɛ nʼankasa mfasoɔ.

Wɔn a wɔnante tee no
 wɔhyɛne asomdwoeɛ mu;
 wɔnya ahomegyeɛ ɛberɛ a wɔadeda sɛ awufoɔ.

Wɔn nnebɔne adufudepɛ maa me bo fuiɛ;
 metwee wɔn aso, na mede abufuo yii mʼani,
 nso wɔkɔɔ so yɛɛ deɛ wɔn akoma pɛ.

Obiara nhwehwɛ atɛntenee;
 obiara mfa nokorɛdie mmɔ ne nkuro.
 Wɔde wɔn ho to nsɛmhuhuo so na wɔtwa nkontonpo;
 wonyinsɛn ɔhaw na wɔwo bɔne.

Wɔtu mmirika kɔyɛ bɔne;
 wɔnkyɛre opira ne awudie ho.
 Baabiara a wɔbɛkɔ no, wɔsɛe hɔ pasaa.

Yɛn nyinaa pɔ so te sɛ sisire;
 yɛde awerɛhoɔ kurum sɛ mmorɔnoma.
 Yɛhwehwɛ atɛntenenee nso yɛnhunu bi;
 ɔgyeɛ nanso ɛwɔ akyirikyiri.

Metiatiaa amanaman no so wɔ mʼabufuo mu;
 memaa wɔboboroe wɔ mʼabufuhyeɛ mu
 na mehwiee wɔn mogya guu fam.”

Ɔkaa sɛ, “Ampa ara wɔyɛ me nkurɔfoɔ,
